➜这位语文课本大红“凡学家”，绯闻缠身还入狱，却被爱了一千多年
http://www.sohu.com/a/435253176_624188	10469
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201130/3d0e1e60d1f140868ded51df323fcfef.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相信各位爱卿最近都学习过<strong>凡尔赛文学</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">总而言之就是用</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>先抑后扬，明贬暗褒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>自问自答，第三人称视角…</strong>等多种手段炫耀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201130/f95f17a4d6a0418c93ce82cc5b871562.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201130/bb9ecbcf50254f7aa758040290fead11.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
